{
  "stem": "22856.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't see any others.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were only in army of German Wehrmacht.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we know that the [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] high command decided to allow Marshal Konev army to liberate our camp.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Schindler decided not to be liberated by the Russians, because they were-- information that he could be separated from us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he decided with a group of eight people to leave the camp a night before.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were clothed in special striped uniforms, in order to remove any threat from unexpected things.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He received, also, a letter signed by three people by Stern, Salpeter, and somebody else, which will-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] certified that he is the liberator of us, that he has received-- he has to receive all help and be saved.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when they left, they of course-- they were close to the American lines.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And everything, then, as we know from the books, was Germany, Israel.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the fact the he expressed the wish to be buried in Israel speaks for itself.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What do you think supported you, sustained you?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Do you think-- was it your Jewish faith that supported you to survive?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes, I was a strong believer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And without having from anybody security promise, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I thoughts in my prayers that Almighty will take care about me and my family, that we will-- in the end, we will reunite.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we will survive the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When you worked for Schindler, did-- who allocated the type of work you were going to do?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, there was an organization in our administration according to the occupation we were registered.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People worked always in, in that area they can be used.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was not compulsory, but that was satisfaction if you could work in your occupation.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
